107class spell_item_mind_amplify_dish : public SpellScript
108{
109 PrepareSpellScript(spell_item_mind_amplify_dish)
110
111 void OnDummyEffect(SpellEffIndex effIndex)
112 {
113 PreventHitDefaultEffect(effIndex);
114
115 Unit* caster = GetCaster();
116 if (Player* player = caster->ToPlayer())
117 {
118 if (Unit* target = GetHitUnit())
119 {
120 // little protection
121 if (target->ToCreature())
122 if (target->ToCreature()->GetCreatureTemplate()->rank > CREATURE_ELITE_NORMAL)
123 return;
124
125 if (GetSpellInfo()->Id != SPELL_AMPLIFY_10S)
126 if (target->getLevel() > 60)
127 return;
128
129 uint8 pct = std::max(0, 20 + player->getLevel() - target->getLevel());
130 if (roll_chance_i(pct))
131 player->CastSpell(target, SPELL_MENTAL_BATTLE, true);
132 else if (roll_chance_i(pct))
133 player->CastSpell(target, GetSpellInfo()->Id == SPELL_AMPLIFY_10S ? SPELL_AMPLIFY_CHARM_10S : SPELL_AMPLIFY_CHARM_30S, true);
134 }
135 }
136 }
137
138 void Register() override
139 {
140 OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_item_mind_amplify_dish::OnDummyEffect, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_DUMMY);
141 }
142};

234class spell_item_with_mount_speed : public AuraScript
235{
236 PrepareAuraScript(spell_item_with_mount_speed);
237
238 bool Validate(SpellInfo const* /*spellInfo*/) override
239 {
240 if (!sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(SPELL_MOUNT_SPEED_CARROT)
241 || !sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(SPELL_MITHRIL_SPURS)
242 || !sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(SPELL_MOUNT_SPEED_RIDING))
243 {
244 return false;
245 }
246 return true;
247 }
248
249 uint32 getMountSpellId()
250 {
251 switch (m_scriptSpellId)
252 {
253 case SPELL_MOUNT_SPEED_CARROT:
254 return SPELL_CARROT_ON_A_STICK_EFFECT;
255 case SPELL_MITHRIL_SPURS:
256 return SPELL_MITHRIL_SPURS_EFFECT;
257 case SPELL_MOUNT_SPEED_RIDING:
258 return SPELL_RIDING_CROP_EFFECT;
259 default:
260 return 0;
261 }
262 }
263
264 void OnApply(AuraEffect const* aurEff, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
265 {
266 Unit* target = GetTarget();
267 if (target->getLevel() <= 70)
268 {
269 if (auto spellId = getMountSpellId())
270 {
271 target->CastSpell(target, spellId, aurEff);
272 }
273 }
274 }
275
276 void OnRemove(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
277 {
278 Unit* target = GetTarget();
279 if (auto spellId = getMountSpellId())
280 {
281 target->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(spellId);
282 }
283 }
284
285 void Register() override
286 {
287 OnEffectApply += AuraEffectApplyFn(spell_item_with_mount_speed::OnApply, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_DUMMY, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL);
288 OnEffectRemove += AuraEffectRemoveFn(spell_item_with_mount_speed::OnRemove, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_DUMMY, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL);
289 }
290};

360class spell_item_sleepy_willy : public SpellScript
361{
362 PrepareSpellScript(spell_item_sleepy_willy);
363
364 void SelectTarget(std::list<WorldObject*>& targets)
365 {
366 Creature* target = nullptr;
367 for (std::list<WorldObject*>::const_iterator itr = targets.begin(); itr != targets.end(); ++itr)
368 if (Creature* creature = (*itr)->ToCreature())
369 if (creature->IsCritter())
370 {
371 target = creature;
372 break;
373 }
374
375 targets.clear();
376 if (target)
377 targets.push_back(target);
378 }
379
380 void HandleScriptEffect(SpellEffIndex effIndex)
381 {
382 PreventHitDefaultEffect(effIndex);
383 Creature* target = GetHitCreature();
384 if (!target)
385 return;
386
387 GetCaster()->CastSpell(target, GetEffectValue(), false);
388 }
389
390 void Register() override
391 {
392 OnObjectAreaTargetSelect += SpellObjectAreaTargetSelectFn(spell_item_sleepy_willy::SelectTarget, EFFECT_0, TARGET_UNIT_SRC_AREA_ENTRY);
393 OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_item_sleepy_willy::HandleScriptEffect, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_SCRIPT_EFFECT);
394 }
395};

604class spell_item_feast : public SpellScript
605{
606 PrepareSpellScript(spell_item_feast);
607
608 bool Load() override
609 {
610 return GetCaster()->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER;
611 }
612
613 void HandleScriptEffect(SpellEffIndex effIndex)
614 {
615 PreventHitDefaultEffect(effIndex);
616
617 Unit* caster = GetCaster();
618 if (Player* player = caster->ToPlayer())
619 {
620 LocaleConstant loc_idx = player->GetSession()->GetSessionDbLocaleIndex();
621
622 switch(GetSpellInfo()->Id)
623 {
624 case SPELL_GREAT_FEAST:
625 if (BroadcastText const* bct = sObjectMgr->GetBroadcastText(GREAT_FEAST_BROADCAST_TEXT_ID_PREPARE))
626 player->TextEmote(bct->GetText(loc_idx, player->getGender()).c_str(), player);
627 break;
628 case SPELL_FISH_FEAST:
629 if (BroadcastText const* bct = sObjectMgr->GetBroadcastText(FISH_FEAST_BROADCAST_TEXT_ID_PREPARE))
630 player->TextEmote(bct->GetText(loc_idx, player->getGender()).c_str(), player);
631 break;
632 case SPELL_SMALL_FEAST:
633 if (BroadcastText const* bct = sObjectMgr->GetBroadcastText(SMALL_FEAST_BROADCAST_TEXT_ID_PREPARE))
634 player->TextEmote(bct->GetText(loc_idx, player->getGender()).c_str(), player);
635 break;
636 case SPELL_GIGANTIC_FEAST:
637 if (BroadcastText const* bct = sObjectMgr->GetBroadcastText(GIGANTIC_FEAST_BROADCAST_TEXT_ID_PREPARE))
638 player->TextEmote(bct->GetText(loc_idx, player->getGender()).c_str(), player);
639 break;
640 }
641 }
642 }
643
644 void Register() override
645 {
646 OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_item_feast::HandleScriptEffect, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_SCRIPT_EFFECT);
647 }
